      "id": "lp-root",
      "name": "Launch Progress",
      "content": "<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 2026-05-17 (Auth P1+P2 + LIVE BOOKS shipped)</p><p></p><p><strong>Overall: 44% complete (21/48 tasks)</strong></p><pre><code>█████████████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░</code></pre><p></p><p><strong>By category:</strong></p><p>Documents &amp; drafts:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 100% <code>████████████████████████</code> 10/10</p><p>Code changes:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 69% <code>████████████████░░░░░░░░</code> 11/16</p><p>Decision docs:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 100% <code>████████████████████████</code> 3/3</p><p>Bug fixes:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 100% <code>████████████████████████</code> 1/1</p><p>Awaiting your decisions: &nbsp;0% <code>░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░</code> 0/5</p><p>External / user-only:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 0% <code>░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░</code> 0/9</p><p>Post-launch (deferred):&nbsp;&nbsp; 0% <code>░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░</code> 0/9</p><p></p><p><strong>Shipped 2026-05-17:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Auth Phase 1 — DONE &amp; verified.</strong> Tier model + env-gated Clerk auth layer; dormant until keys are set.</p></li><li><p><strong>Auth Phase 2 — DONE.</strong> Billing scaffolding: env-gated Stripe + RevenueCat, dormant until keys. (Phase 3 = tier enforcement #33 still pending.)</p></li><li><p><strong>LIVE BOOKS — BUILT &amp; shipped.</strong> Generalized transform engine; documented in all 4 places; core surface runtime-proven by a new automated test (dialog/scope/preview/auto-apply-off/merge-overwrite all pass). Residual: live AI refresh round-trip + post-refresh diff cards not yet automation-covered (medium follow-up #57).</p></li><li><p><strong>Language translation (#52) de-risked</strong> — LIVE BOOKS shipped the shared transform engine it plugs into.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Gemini 4 prep (#49) — DONE, waiting on May 19 Google I/O keynote:</strong> registry refactor, default bump to gemini-2.5-flash (23 call sites), launch-automation script, day-of runbook all committed. Only keynote-day execution remains.</p><p><strong>Infra:</strong> project relocated out of iCloud to ~/Developer/IdiamPro (machine-load problem permanently resolved); git auth moved to macOS Keychain.</p><p><strong>TEST EVERYTHING 2026-05-17: 38/38 on clean runs</strong> (electron 8/8, gemma4 6/6, mcp 24/24); relocated repo validated healthy.</p>",
